NK013(pa)009:0: dpal gsang ba'i snying po rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu
NK013(pa)009:1: 'phrul zhi ba'i sgrub thabs rnam grol shing rta zhes
NK013(pa)009:2: bya ba bzhugs / dpal gsang ba'i snying po rdo
NK013(pa)009:3: rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i sgrub thabs rnam
NK013(pa)009:4: grol shing rta zhes bya ba lhag pa ting nge
NK013(pa)009:6: thabs las thabs gyur bde chen sgyu ma ni //
NK013(pa)009:7: rnam thar gsum ldan btsun mo'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK013(pa)009:8: gdan gsum sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i mngon rtogs la //
NK013(pa)009:9: yid chos gnyis su med pa'i phyag gis btud //
NK013(pa)009:10: de la rgyud thams cad kyi spyi //
NK013(pa)009:12: man ngag thams cad kyi mdzod khang /
NK013(pa)009:13: tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad kyi rtsa bar gyur pas o
NK013(pa)009:14: rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pas kyang man ngag lta ba'i
NK013(pa)009:15: phreng bar ched du brjod cing basngagasa la /
NK013(pa)009:16: slob dpon bi ma la dang /
NK013(pa)009:18: rma gnyag la sogs pa'i lo pan rgyal ba'i zhal
NK013(pa)009:19: skyin rnams kyis bshad sgrub kyis gtan la phab pa
NK013(pa)009:20: dpal gsang ba'i snying po rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu
NK013(pa)009:22: zhi ba rin po che'i sgrub thabs rnam grol shing rta bstan pa la gsum /
NK013(pa)009:26: dang po la'ang dkyil 'khor 'du bya ba dang /
NK013(pa)009:27: cho ga'i sbyor ba gnyis las /
NK013(pa)009:29: dbang sgrub chen mo'i rigs dang 'brel na sa'i cho
NK013(pa)009:30: ga nas bzung rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i
NK013(pa)009:31: las rim gzhan du shes par bya zhing /
NK013(pa)009:32: sgrub mchod 'jug pa de tsam la ni rdul tshon
NK013(pa)009:33: gyi sgos chos rnams dor ba'i ras bril la'ang brten
NK013(pa)009:34: du rung ngo // gnyis pa la rnam grangs bdun las /
NK013(pa)009:35: dang po rgyud dag par bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:36: spyi phyag dang gral phyag sngon du 'gro bas /
NK013(pa)009:37: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni /
NK013(pa)009:39: nongs pa mchis na'ang rab nongs bzod par gsol /
NK013(pa)009:40: zhes dmigs 'don zung du chud par bya'o //
NK013(pa)009:41: gnyis pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:42: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK013(pa)009:43: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:44: mchog gsum bstan pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK013(pa)009:45: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK013(pa)009:46: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:47: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:48: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK013(pa)009:49: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:50: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK013(pa)009:51: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK013(pa)009:52: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK013(pa)009:53: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK013(pa)009:54: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK013(pa)009:55: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul lo //
NK013(pa)009:56: tshe rabs bgrangs ba'i dge ba rnams //
NK013(pa)009:57: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK013(pa)009:58: lan gsum gyis rjes tshogs zhing rang la bsdu'o //
NK013(pa)009:59: gsum pa sngags sdom bzung zhing dam bca' ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:60: hohrdzogasa sangs rin chen dag pa'i sems nyid dang //
NK013(pa)009:61: rtogs pa'i dri ma rab bral dam pa'i chos //
NK013(pa)009:62: brtul zhugs bzang po'i tshogs la skyabs su mchi //
NK013(pa)009:63: srid dang bral ba rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK013(pa)009:64: deng nas bdag ni 'gro kun nyer 'tsho'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:65: mgon rnams 'bangs su bdag nyid 'bul lags kyi //
NK013(pa)009:66: brtse ba'i thugs rjes bzhes par mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)009:67: byams pa'i zhal bzang dus 'dir gzigs nas kyang /
NK013(pa)009:69: / 'gal 'khrul nyams chag thams cad bskang du gsol //
NK013(pa)009:70: ji ltar sngon gyi rgyal ba sras bcas dang //
NK013(pa)009:71: rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK013(pa)009:72: phyi nang gsang ba mchog gi dam tshig dang //
NK013(pa)009:73: sdom pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas bzung ba ltar //
NK013(pa)009:74: deng nas bdag kyang lam chen der zhugs te /
NK013(pa)009:76: / 'gro la phan phyir de dag gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:77: gdod nas ma skyes mkha' ltar rnam dag cing //
NK013(pa)009:78: mi 'gyur lhun grub rang byung 'od gsal la //
NK013(pa)009:79: ji bzhin ma bcos chos nyid don bsgom ste //
NK013(pa)009:80: chos sku yangs pa chen po'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK013(pa)009:81: kun bzang don gyi dam tshig gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:82: bde bar gshegs pa rigs kyi dam tshig tu //
NK013(pa)009:83: sdom dang chos sdud sems can don byed cing //
NK013(pa)009:84: byang chub snying po rang la mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:85: chos kyi 'khor lo'i rdzas kyang gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:86: mi 'gyur rdo rje rigs kyi dam tshig tu //
NK013(pa)009:87: rang bzhin bskyed rdzogs don las mi 'da' zhing //
NK013(pa)009:88: rdo rje slob dpon mchog tu bkur ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:89: thabs dang shes rab rang la mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:90: rdo rje dril bu'i rdzas kyang gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:91: bsam 'phel rin chen rigs kyi dam tshig tu //
NK013(pa)009:92: sbyin pa rnam bzhis 'gro kun bskyang ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:93: bsod nams ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs byed cing //
NK013(pa)009:94: lhun grub yon tan rang la mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:95: nor bu rin chen rdzas kyang gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:96: ma chags pad+ma rigs kyi dam tshig tu //
NK013(pa)009:97: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos rnams yongs gzung zhing /
NK013(pa)009:99: / 'gro la tshad med snying rjes chags pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:100: skyon bral chos nyid rang la mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:101: yid 'ong pad+ma mchog kyang gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:102: sna tshogs las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig tu //
NK013(pa)009:103: theg gsum sdom pa mtha' dag bzung ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:104: don gnyis lhun grub rang la mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:105: rgya gram ral gri mchog kyang gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:106: bla med rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig tu //
NK013(pa)009:107: zung 'jug lam du thams cad bslang ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:108: spang blang med pa'i rol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:109: kha t+w+aam thod pa cang te'u gzung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:110: mdor na gang gis 'khor ba rnam sbyong ba //
NK013(pa)009:111: phung po skye mched khams rnams dag byed cing //
NK013(pa)009:112: dbang po'i yul dang nyon mongs rnam sbyong ba //
NK013(pa)009:113: sku lnga ye shes lnga dang gsung lnga dang //
NK013(pa)009:114: yon tan phrin las rigs lnga sgrub pa'i rdzas //
NK013(pa)009:115: nang gi dgongs spyod rgya mtsho mtha' yas dang //
NK013(pa)009:116: phyi rol dam rdzas 'dod yon thabs chen lnga //
NK013(pa)009:117: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:118: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig lnga rnam la //
NK013(pa)009:119: rdo rje mchog sgrub sku gsung thugs gsum dang //
NK013(pa)009:120: shes dang mi spang dang du blang ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:121: bsgrub dang spyad par bya ba lnga lnga ste //
NK013(pa)009:122: nyi shu rtsa brgyad rtsa ba yan lag bcas //
NK013(pa)009:123: gsang sngags rdo rje snying po'i sdom pa kun //
NK013(pa)009:124: deng nas brtsams te bdag gis bsrung bar bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:125: gang la brten nas srid pa rnam sbyong zhing //
NK013(pa)009:126: zhi ba thar pa'i dam pa thabs chen kun /
NK013(pa)009:128: / 'gro ba'i don du bdag gis yongs su gzung //
NK013(pa)009:129: srid zhir mi gnas byang chub mchog zhugs te //
NK013(pa)009:130: dkyil 'khor dbang phyug rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK013(pa)009:131: dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma kun mchod pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:132: tshogs gnyis brtson pa mtha' yas rgya mtsho bsgrub /
NK013(pa)009:134: / 'gro la snying brtse phan pa mchog tu bya //
NK013(pa)009:135: gnod par mi bya brnyas par yang mi bgyi //
NK013(pa)009:136: gcig pu zhi ba don du mi gnyer zhing //
NK013(pa)009:137: gzhan don yang dag bsgrub la brtson pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:138: rang gzhan thar pa'i sgo ni dbye bar bgyi /
NK013(pa)009:139: bzhi pa phyi rol bskrad pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:140: gzhi bgegs so sor gtor ma cha gnyis bshams la /
NK013(pa)009:142: h'u yul phyogs 'di dag kun la gnas pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:143: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po 'byung po dang //
NK013(pa)009:144: yi dwags sha za brjod byed smyo byed dang //
NK013(pa)009:145: mkha' 'gro ma mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK013(pa)009:146: mchod sbyin gtor ma bzang po 'di nyid bzhes //
NK013(pa)009:147: bar du gcod pa'i bsam sbyor kun spang la //
NK013(pa)009:148: zhi dang phan pa'i sems kyis gnas par gyis //
NK013(pa)009:149: h'u ye shes rol pa dpal gyi skur gsal zhing //
NK013(pa)009:150: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i khro tshogs kyis //
NK013(pa)009:151: bgegs rigs ma lus rgya mtsho'i mthar bskrad do //
NK013(pa)009:153: lnga pa srung 'khor ni 'od rim las /
NK013(pa)009:154: h'u stong chen gsal ba'i rig pa nyid //
NK013(pa)009:155: skad cig sa bon rang gi lhar //
NK013(pa)009:157: zhe sdang rdo rjer gsal ba yi //
NK013(pa)009:158: thugs kyi sa bon 'od zer las //
NK013(pa)009:159: mtshon cha rim spros bar chad bskrad //
NK013(pa)009:161: dz+wa la ram gyis me dpung 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:162: rnam rtog 'du shes kun spangs na //
NK013(pa)009:163: bgegs kyi sbyor ba yong mi 'gyur //
NK013(pa)009:164: de bas rnam rtog gegs yin pas //
NK013(pa)009:165: yang dag rig pa nyid kyis srung //
NK013(pa)009:167: chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i klong nas ye shes kyi 'khor lo sku phyag rgya /
NK013(pa)009:169: thugs phyag mtshan gyi rnam par sad pa bdag gnas yo byad rnams la thim par bsam la /
NK013(pa)009:172: b+ha ga w+aan sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)009:173: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)009:174: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)009:175: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)009:176: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)009:177: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)009:178: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)009:180: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)009:181: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)009:182: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)009:183: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:184: rol mo sna chogs kyi sgra sbyar zhing h'u h'u h'u h'u gis byin bsdus /
NK013(pa)009:185: bdun pa mchod rdzas brlab pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:187: bdag nyid lhar gsal thugs ka'i h'u yig las //
NK013(pa)009:188: ram yam kham 'phros ye shes me rlung chus //
NK013(pa)009:189: mchod rdzas dngos 'dzin skyon sbyangs stong pa'i ngang //
NK013(pa)009:190: a las stong gsum b+han+d+hara rdzogs pa'i nang /
NK013(pa)009:192: / 'khor 'das bcud drangs h'u las nyer spyod kyi //
NK013(pa)009:193: dam rdzas 'dod yon sprin phung rgya mtshor gyur //
NK013(pa)009:194: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya dang /
NK013(pa)009:200: rdo rje zhabs bsil ma la sogs pa mchod pa'i lha mos nam mkha' gang bar gyur /
NK013(pa)009:202: stong pa'i ngang las kam yig yongs gyur las //
NK013(pa)009:203: mi mgo'i sgyed steng a las b+han+d+ha'i nang /
NK013(pa)009:205: / 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte bar bcas pa'i dbus //
NK013(pa)009:206: go ku da ha na las sha lnga dang //
NK013(pa)009:207: bi mu ma ra shu las bdud rtsi lnga //
NK013(pa)009:208: rang rang sa bon gyis mtshan yam ram las //
NK013(pa)009:209: rlung g.yos me sbar dam rdzas zhu ba'i steng //
NK013(pa)009:210: h'u s+w+aa am h+aa las phyag mtshan lnga //
NK013(pa)009:211: so sos yu ba byas pa'i dril bu rnams //
NK013(pa)009:212: yongs gyur rigs lnga yab yum mnyam sbyor gyur /
NK013(pa)009:213: h'u t+r+aam h+r+aihah m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam /
NK013(pa)009:214: zla ba'i kha gcod sna tshogs rdo rje'i lter //
NK013(pa)009:215: rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma rgya gram 'dzin //
NK013(pa)009:216: ra bzhir yum bzhi rdo rje'i tog gi dbus //
NK013(pa)009:217: stangs dpyal kun gyi bde ba'i 'od rlangs sprin //
NK013(pa)009:218: dbyangs gsal las gyur 'bru gsum brtsegs ma yi /
NK013(pa)009:220: / 'od kyis rgyal ba mchod cing gzhan don byas //
NK013(pa)009:221: tshur 'dus dam tshig rdzas dang dbyer med 'dres //
NK013(pa)009:222: ye shes bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur //
NK013(pa)009:223: mtheb srin rta mgrin yab yum du gsal bas bdud rtsi dkrug cing /
NK013(pa)009:224: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aah nyer gcig dang /
NK013(pa)009:228: stong pa'i ngang las gtor gzhong pad+ma'i snod //
NK013(pa)009:229: gtor rdzas mchog chen mi dang seng ge glang //
NK013(pa)009:230: ba lang rta sha bdud rtsi lnga yi steng //
NK013(pa)009:231: rigs lnga yab yum phyag mtshan rnams kyis mtshan /
NK013(pa)009:233: / 'og nas rlung g.yos me sbar bdud rtsi khol //
NK013(pa)009:234: zag med ro brgya ldan pa'i gtor ma ni //
NK013(pa)009:235: dbang po drug la dgyes dgu'i sprin du gyur /
NK013(pa)009:236: +aahmh'u ma h+aa ba l+aing+ta te dz+wa ba lim ta
NK013(pa)009:237: ba la b+aa te gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa
NK013(pa)009:241: a las yum mkha' rnams thar gsum ldan dbyings //
NK013(pa)009:242: ma las nyi dkyil ra yig yongs gyur las //
NK013(pa)009:243: chags chen srid pa'i rak+ta 'bar ba'i klong //
NK013(pa)009:244: ngar 'dzin r+au tra'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad rnams //
NK013(pa)009:245: thabs mchog rdo rje nor bus sbyangs pa yis /
NK013(pa)009:247: / 'khor ba lugs ldog skye med chos skur bsgral //
NK013(pa)009:248: zeg ma'i tshogs la zhing gi lhu dum dang //
NK013(pa)009:249: rdo rje sgeg mo'i mchod sprin spro bar gyur //
NK013(pa)009:250: +aahmh'u ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+dala la h'u h+r+aihth+aah lan gsum /
NK013(pa)009:251: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la theg pa chen po'i lam
NK013(pa)009:252: gyi rtsa ba byang chub chen por sems bskyed pa
NK013(pa)009:253: dang / phyin drug gi yan lag bskyed rjogs kyi dngos por sdud pa'o //
NK013(pa)009:254: dang po la kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis las /
NK013(pa)009:255: dang por chos dang sems can la dmigs pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:256: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK013(pa)009:257: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK013(pa)009:258: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK013(pa)009:259: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK013(pa)009:260: gnyis pa dmigs med rnam par smin pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:261: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)009:262: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)009:263: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK013(pa)009:264: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK013(pa)009:265: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)009:266: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK013(pa)009:270: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)009:271: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)009:272: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK013(pa)009:273: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK013(pa)009:274: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)009:275: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)009:276: dmigs pa med las thabs cad dmigs //
NK013(pa)009:277: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK013(pa)009:278: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)009:279: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK013(pa)009:284: gnyis pa la ting 'dzin gsum gyis bskyed gzhi bsten pa /
NK013(pa)009:285: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK013(pa)009:286: phrin las bya ba'i yan lag bsgrub pa'o //
NK013(pa)009:288: dang po rdo rje lta bu de bzhin nyid ni /
NK013(pa)009:289: gzhi rgyud bde gshegs snying po'i dag bya tshogs brgyad glo bur ba'i spros pa bsal la /
NK013(pa)009:290: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK013(pa)009:291: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK013(pa)009:292: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK013(pa)009:293: de phyir dngos po med pa'o //
NK013(pa)009:294: gnyis pa dpa' bar 'gro ba kun snang ni /
NK013(pa)009:295: chos nyid de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams
NK013(pa)009:296: la stong nyid spros pa med pa'i gdangs dmigs med
NK013(pa)009:298: de bzhin nyid ni spros med kyang //
NK013(pa)009:299: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)009:300: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:301: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK013(pa)009:302: gsum pa sgyu ma lta bu rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK013(pa)009:303: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa de'i ngang
NK013(pa)009:304: las yid byed pa po kun tu bzang po'i bdag
NK013(pa)009:305: nyid skye med kyi yi ger ldang bste /
NK013(pa)009:306: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK013(pa)009:308: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK013(pa)009:309: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK013(pa)009:310: sems nyid ye ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK013(pa)009:311: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK013(pa)009:312: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK013(pa)009:313: de ltar skye med kyi yi ge las spro bsdu'i
NK013(pa)009:314: tshig tu bstan kyang 'phel 'grib ltar snang ba ni
NK013(pa)009:315: med de / chos nyid kyi don yig 'brus mtshon
NK013(pa)009:316: nas bskyed rim gyi rol rtsal mtha' dag chos bya
NK013(pa)009:317: ba mo kun tu bzang mo lhag mthong gsal ba'i
NK013(pa)009:318: bdag nyid du brtan par bya ba ste /
NK013(pa)009:319: +aahraba tu brtan gyur a dkar las //
NK013(pa)009:320: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro //
NK013(pa)009:321: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK013(pa)009:323: de las ming tshogs gsal 'gyur kun //
NK013(pa)009:324: spro zhing bsdu ba'ang de bzhin no /
NK013(pa)009:326: / 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi //
NK013(pa)009:327: brtan 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK013(pa)009:328: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang dang brten pa lha bsgom pa gnyis kyi /
NK013(pa)009:330: dang po rten gzhi 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor sgom pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:331: a las mtha' dbus med pa yi /
NK013(pa)009:334: de nas yam las byung ba yi //
NK013(pa)009:335: rlung gi dkyil 'khor bsam par bya //
NK013(pa)009:336: de steng yi ge ram las ni //
NK013(pa)009:337: me yi dkyil 'khor bskyed par bya //
NK013(pa)009:338: de yi steng du bam bsams te //
NK013(pa)009:339: de las chu yi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK013(pa)009:340: chu yi dkyil 'khor steng du ni //
NK013(pa)009:341: lam las ye shes sa gzhir brtag /
NK013(pa)009:342: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang sgom pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:344: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK013(pa)009:345: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK013(pa)009:346: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK013(pa)009:350: gru chad bzhis brgyan par khyams dang //
NK013(pa)009:351: kun tu gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan //
NK013(pa)009:352: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK013(pa)009:353: zhes pas sdug bsngal bden pa'i rang gzugs snod ltar
NK013(pa)009:354: snang ba'i kun 'byung ba can las snod ma dag
NK013(pa)009:355: pa rten gzhal yas khang gis 'gog pa'i lam gyi
NK013(pa)009:356: bden pa ni / lhun po'i steng du /
NK013(pa)009:357: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+dala b+h+r+aam /
NK013(pa)009:358: b+h+r+aum yig yongs su gyur pa las /
NK013(pa)009:359: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang
NK013(pa)009:360: gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa nang nas rim pa bzhin
NK013(pa)009:365: ljang ba'i rin po che'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang ldan pa'i steng na /
NK013(pa)009:366: rin po che'i pha gu ser po rin po che
NK013(pa)009:367: sna tshogs pas bkra ba 'phyar thabs su bkod pa'i
NK013(pa)009:368: mthar mu tig gi mgul 'khor 'phyang ba /
NK013(pa)009:369: de'i steng na bre phul gyi snam bu la gser
NK013(pa)009:370: gyi ska rags bzhi'i phyi ngos su ma ka ra'i
NK013(pa)009:371: kha nas rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang /
NK013(pa)009:375: zla ba rlung gis skyod pa la sogs pas mdzes pa /
NK013(pa)009:376: de'i phyi ngos su bya 'dabs la 'phyang ba'i rin po che'i shar bu /
NK013(pa)009:377: steng ngos su mda' yab pad+ma 'dab ma phyed pa'i dbyibs can /
NK013(pa)009:378: de dag gi bar bar du bum pa la gnas pa'i rgyal mtshan dang /
NK013(pa)009:380: zur bzhir rnam par bkra ba'i gdugs kyis mtshan pa /
NK013(pa)009:381: rtsig pa'i 'gram nas 'dod yon gyi snam bu dmar
NK013(pa)009:382: pos bskor ba la gzugs rdo rje ma la sogs
NK013(pa)009:383: lha mo rnams kyis mchod pa'i sprin rab 'byams spro
NK013(pa)009:384: ba / sgo dang sgo khyud kyi mtshams dang zur
NK013(pa)009:385: bzhir zla ba phyed pa la gnas pa'i rdo rje
NK013(pa)009:387: sgo logs kyi zur bzhi nas bum pa la gnas pa'i ka ba bzhi bzhes btegs pa'i rta babs /
NK013(pa)009:388: rta rkang chu skyes rin chen sgrom //
NK013(pa)009:389: sna 'phyang bzhi las za ra tshags //
NK013(pa)009:390: rin chen sgril 'phyang shar bu khyung //
NK013(pa)009:391: zhes pas rim pa can gyi snam bu brgyad pa
NK013(pa)009:392: bsil khang dang ldan pa'i rtse mor pad+ma la gnas
NK013(pa)009:393: pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo g.yas g.yon du ri dwags
NK013(pa)009:394: pho mo dang bcas pa gzhan yang gdugs dang rgyal
NK013(pa)009:395: mtshan ba dan sna tshogs pa dang gser gyi dril
NK013(pa)009:396: bu la sogs pas brgyan pa /
NK013(pa)009:397: sgo'i g.yas g.yon gyi gzhi la t+aa la'i ljon pa dang /
NK013(pa)009:398: dpag bsam gyi shing la bkra shis pa'i bya snyan par sgrog pa sna tshogs gnas pa /
NK013(pa)009:399: shing de dag kyang gser gyi tha gus bres shing
NK013(pa)009:400: dril bu dang g.yer kha chos kyi sgra snyan par
NK013(pa)009:402: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i khrus kyi rdzing bu la lha mo sna tshogs bde bar brtse ba /
NK013(pa)009:403: rin po che'i phung po 'od 'bar ba re re ste brgyad dang /
NK013(pa)009:404: gzhan yang rin po che sna bdun dang /
NK013(pa)009:405: bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad sogs 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad kyis mdzes par gang ba'o //
NK013(pa)009:406: gzhal yas khang gi nang bar khyams gru bzhi pas kun nas bskor zhing /
NK013(pa)009:407: gru chad bzhi glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa'i nang du /
NK013(pa)009:408: rdo rje'i phreng bas bskor ba'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK013(pa)009:409: pa lte ba dang bcas pa rnams rim pa bzhin
NK013(pa)009:410: khyad par du gyur pas 'phags pa rdo rje'i zlum
NK013(pa)009:411: bskor la brten pa'i ka ba rigs kyi mtshan ma
NK013(pa)009:412: can gnyis gnyis kyis phyogs re nas bteg pa'i steng
NK013(pa)009:413: / rdo rje'i gdung gis mig mngas ris su bris
NK013(pa)009:414: shing mdzes par phub pa'i dbus phyur bu sangs rgyas
NK013(pa)009:415: kyi gtsug tor ltar kun nas zlum por 'khyil ba'i
NK013(pa)009:416: rtse mo rdo rje rin po che'i tog stong 'od
NK013(pa)009:417: zer mtha' yas pa spro bas mdzes pa /
NK013(pa)009:418: nang gi steng dang 'og gi gzhi thams cad shar dkar /
NK013(pa)009:423: lha dang mi las khyad par du gyur pa'i ngo
NK013(pa)009:424: mtshar du mas 'phags pa'i gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid
NK013(pa)009:425: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa dngas shing bsgrib pa
NK013(pa)009:426: med par kun tu gsal ba gzhi tshad med pa'i
NK013(pa)009:427: ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba la rdzogs par
NK013(pa)009:428: gyur / gsum pa gdan bskyed pa ni rgyud las /
NK013(pa)009:429: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK013(pa)009:430: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK013(pa)009:431: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK013(pa)009:433: gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi lte ba dang rtsibs bzhir rim pa bzhin /
NK013(pa)009:438: byang du mkha' lding rnams kyis bteg pa'i rin po
NK013(pa)009:439: che'i khri bkod pa phul du byung ba'i steng du
NK013(pa)009:443: sna tshogs pad+ma'i lte bar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK013(pa)009:444: zla ba nya gang ba ste lnga brtsegs /
NK013(pa)009:450: pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan sum brtsegs /
NK013(pa)009:451: 'khyams kyi shar nub gnyis su rin po che'i khrir /
NK013(pa)009:455: pad nyi zla ba'i gdan bzhi brtsegs /
NK013(pa)009:458: sna tshogs pad+ma'i gdan re re sgo bzhir /
NK013(pa)009:460: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)009:461: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la gsum las /
NK013(pa)009:463: gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul /
NK013(pa)009:465: / 'khor lo rgyal po rgyal mo dang //
NK013(pa)009:466: g.yas nas mthong thos snom pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:467: myong dang btsun mo'i tshogs su bcas //
NK013(pa)009:468: gru chad la ni mthong byed dang //
NK013(pa)009:469: thos byed snom byed myong byed rnams //
NK013(pa)009:470: btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas par gnas //
NK013(pa)009:471: bar khyams la ni thub drug dang //
NK013(pa)009:472: mdun dang rgyab tu byed pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:473: bya ba dag ni gnas par bstan //
NK013(pa)009:474: sgo khyud bzhi la 'joms pa ni //
NK013(pa)009:475: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK013(pa)009:476: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK013(pa)009:477: pad+ma ral gri dril bu dang //
NK013(pa)009:478: ut+pala klu shing la sogs mtshan //
NK013(pa)009:479: mdzes tshul mnyes pa'i yo byad 'dzin //
NK013(pa)009:480: mthing ga dkar po ser le brgan //
NK013(pa)009:481: ljang gu la sogs sna tshogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:482: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK013(pa)009:483: gsal 'tsher lhun sdug gzi byin ldan /
NK013(pa)009:488: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:489: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)009:490: ces pas sbyang gzhi phung khams skye mched lhar shar
NK013(pa)009:491: ba'i bcud ma dag pa dang kun brtags kyi rtog
NK013(pa)009:492: tshogs lha skur bsgrub pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:493: gzhi'i a yig las yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK013(pa)009:494: thon te so so'i gdan steng du 'khod pa ni
NK013(pa)009:504: rtsibs mchan gyi shar lho'i gdan la /
NK013(pa)009:512: gru chad kyi shar lho'i gdan la /
NK013(pa)009:543: rnams rang rang gi lha'i kha dog dang mthun par
NK013(pa)009:544: so so'i gdan la 'khod pa'i mthar a zhes brjod
NK013(pa)009:545: pas / gzhi'i a de yig 'bru rnams la khyab
NK013(pa)009:546: par thim pas shin tu gsal zhing 'bar bar bsam
NK013(pa)009:547: pas / la / a nyid sna tshogs par snang ba'i //
NK013(pa)009:548: ka la sogs pa bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK013(pa)009:549: sgra yi ming gis thams cad bsdus //
NK013(pa)009:550: mngon rdzogs rgyal po de nyid nges //
NK013(pa)009:551: a s+pha ra na phata ces brjod pas yig 'bru
NK013(pa)009:552: rnams las 'od zer 'phros sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa
NK013(pa)009:553: bsgrub / sam ha ra na h'u slar 'dus nas
NK013(pa)009:554: yig 'bru rnams la thim pa 'od du zhu ba
NK013(pa)009:555: bsgrub / las / badz+ra tsakra rat+na pad+ma khang+ga g+han+ta zhes brjod pas /
NK013(pa)009:556: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:557: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:558: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:559: nub tu pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:560: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:561: rtsibs mchan gyi shar lhor rin po che'i myu gu dang me long /
NK013(pa)009:562: lho nub tu ral gri dang phreng ba /
NK013(pa)009:563: nub byang du pad+ma dang pi wang /
NK013(pa)009:564: byang shar du rdo rje dang rnga yab /
NK013(pa)009:565: gru chad bzhi'i shar lhor klu shing dang spos khang /
NK013(pa)009:566: lho nub tu pusti dang me tog /
NK013(pa)009:567: nub byang du rin po che'i snye ma dang mar me /
NK013(pa)009:568: byang shar du ut+pala dang dri chab /
NK013(pa)009:569: khyams kyi shar du rdo rje /
NK013(pa)009:577: shar sgor n+ri mgo gdengs pa dang lcags kyu /
NK013(pa)009:578: lho sgor rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK013(pa)009:579: nub sgor thod pa sbrul gyis dkris pa dang lcags sgrog /
NK013(pa)009:580: byang du rdo rje rgya gram dang dril bu ste phyag mtshan bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gyur /
NK013(pa)009:583: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrub /
NK013(pa)009:584: sam ha ra na h'u slar 'dus nas phyag mtshan rnams la thim pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK013(pa)009:586: dkyil 'khor chen po'i dbus dag tu //
NK013(pa)009:587: bdag nyid bcom ldan mi bskyod pa //
NK013(pa)009:589: sku gsung thugs kyi dbu gsum ni //
NK013(pa)009:590: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK013(pa)009:591: ye shes drug gi phyag nyid la //
NK013(pa)009:592: rdo rje pad+ma ral gri ni //
NK013(pa)009:593: g.yas kyi phyag na bsnams par mdzad //
NK013(pa)009:595: g.yon gyi ye shes phyag na bsnams //
NK013(pa)009:596: g.yas pas rdo rje thugs kar brten //
NK013(pa)009:597: g.yon pa dril bu yum la 'khyud //
NK013(pa)009:598: thabs dang shes rab zhabs gnyis ni //
NK013(pa)009:599: mnyam pa'i btul zhugs skyil mo krung //
NK013(pa)009:600: mdun dang rgyab med kun tu zhal //
NK013(pa)009:601: mtshan dang dpe byad kun gyis spras /
NK013(pa)009:605: rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan cing //
NK013(pa)009:606: sna tshogs rgyan rnams kun gyis brgyan //
NK013(pa)009:607: btsun mo snang ba'i dbyings phyug ma //
NK013(pa)009:608: gzhon tshul 'khril ldem shin tu chags //
NK013(pa)009:609: cha lugs la sogs yab dang mthun //
NK013(pa)009:610: g.yon pa dril bu thugs kar brten //
NK013(pa)009:611: g.yas pa nyi ma las la 'khril //
NK013(pa)009:612: gnyis ka'ang lha rdzas kyi dar dkar po gser gyi
NK013(pa)009:613: ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs dang tshi gu'i smad
NK013(pa)009:614: dkris / kha dog sna tshogs pa'i cod pan zi ldir /
NK013(pa)009:615: gar gyi phu rung ste dar gyi chas gos lnga dang /
NK013(pa)009:622: phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu ste rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis mdzes par spras pa /
NK013(pa)009:623: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can /
NK013(pa)009:624: gsal mtsher lhun sdug gzi byin 'bar ba ste /
NK013(pa)009:625: zhi ba'i nyams dgus brgyan pa /
NK013(pa)009:626: 'od zer kha dog drug re re yang bye ba
NK013(pa)009:627: phrag drug drug tu 'phro zhing 'bar ba'i klong na
NK013(pa)009:628: bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o
NK013(pa)009:630: shar gyi rtsibs la rnam snang dkar po /
NK013(pa)009:631: dkar mthing dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK013(pa)009:632: po gnyis kyis 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pas
NK013(pa)009:634: bar pas rdo rje dang rin po che /
NK013(pa)009:635: tha chas pad+ma dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:637: yum spyan ma dkar mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK013(pa)009:640: lhor rin chen 'byung ldan ser po /
NK013(pa)009:641: ser dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rin po che dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:642: bar pas 'khor lo dang rdo rje /
NK013(pa)009:643: tha mas pad+ma dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:645: m+aa ma k+ai ser mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK013(pa)009:648: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas dmar po /
NK013(pa)009:649: dmar dkar sngo ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:650: bar pas 'khor lo dang rin po che /
NK013(pa)009:651: tha mas rdo rje dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:653: gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK013(pa)009:656: byang du don yod grub pa ljang gu /
NK013(pa)009:657: ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis ral gri dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)009:658: bar pas 'khor lo dang rin po che /
NK013(pa)009:659: tha mas pad+ma dang rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:661: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang gu g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK013(pa)009:662: g.yon ral gri 'dzin pa yab rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung dang /
NK013(pa)009:663: yul rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis rol ba'o //
NK013(pa)009:665: rtsibs mchan bzhi'i shar lhor sa snying dkar po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu 'dzin zhing /
NK013(pa)009:666: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK013(pa)009:667: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)009:668: sgeg mo dkar mo g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK013(pa)009:671: lho nub tu nam snying ser po g.yas ral gri 'dzin zhing /
NK013(pa)009:672: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK013(pa)009:673: t+r+aam m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoh phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:674: h+r+aihh+aa h'u pad+ma pra da ma /
NK013(pa)009:675: nub byang du spyan ras gzigs dmar po g.yas pad+ma dkar po 'dzin zhing /
NK013(pa)009:676: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK013(pa)009:677: h+r+aimhg+ai ti r+aa go hamh glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:679: byang shar du phyag rdor mthing ga g.yas rdo rje 'dzin zhing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK013(pa)009:680: am nirti r+aa ga ya mye /
NK013(pa)009:681: gar ma ljang gu gar rgya mdzad pa /
NK013(pa)009:682: mee d+h+aa ra ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:683: gru chad bzhi'i shar lhor byams pa dkar ser g.yas klu shing 'dzin zhing /
NK013(pa)009:684: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK013(pa)009:686: bdug spos ma dkar ser spos khang 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:687: th+l+hi nims+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:688: lho nub tu sgrib sel dmar ser g.yas chos kyi 'khor lo 'dzin zhing /
NK013(pa)009:689: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK013(pa)009:691: me tog ma dmar ser me tog gi phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:692: h'u swa ra dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:693: nub byang du kun bzang dmar ljang g.yas rin po che'i snye ma 'dzin zhing /
NK013(pa)009:694: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK013(pa)009:695: b+aam d+ai ba su gi ri /
NK013(pa)009:696: mar me ma dmar ljang mar me 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:697: m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:698: byang shar du 'jam dpal dkar ljang g.yas ut+pala 'dzin zhing /
NK013(pa)009:699: g.yon dril bu dkur brten la /
NK013(pa)009:701: dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung phor 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:702: sems dpa' brgyad po thams cad kyang zhabs g.yas cung zad brkyang ba'i phyed skyil gyis bzhugs shing /
NK013(pa)009:703: sems ma rnams g.yon cung zad brkyang ba'i phyed skyil gyis yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK013(pa)009:705: khyams kyi shar du kun tu bzang po mthing ga
NK013(pa)009:706: mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can rdo rje'i skyil mo
NK013(pa)009:708: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta +aah nub
NK013(pa)009:709: tu kun tu bzang mo mthing ga g.yon steng du
NK013(pa)009:710: bzhag pa'i mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can pad+ma'i skyil
NK013(pa)009:711: krung gis bzhugs pa gshegs pa gshegs ma sems dpa'
NK013(pa)009:712: sems ma kun bzang yab yum rnams zhi ba'i rgyan
NK013(pa)009:713: chas bcu gsum gyis mdzes shing /
NK013(pa)009:714: tshul dgu'i nyams kyis rgyas pa'o //
NK013(pa)009:716: khyams kyi shar lhor lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:718: byang du lha min gyi thub pa mthing ga go cha 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:720: lhor mi'i thub pa ser po gseg par 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:722: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa dmar po pusti 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:724: lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:726: bya shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:727: drug ka'ang gtsug tor dang ldan zhing tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can /
NK013(pa)009:728: 'gro ba'i don la 'greng stabs su gshegs pa'i tshul can no //
NK013(pa)009:730: shar sgor gshin rje gshed smug nag n+ri mgo gdengs pa 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:731: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:732: lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK013(pa)009:734: lho sgor stobs po che ser nag rdo rje rtse lnga 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:735: ma h+aa ra t+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:736: zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK013(pa)009:738: nub sgor rta mgrin dmar nag thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:739: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:740: lcags sgrog ma dmar nag lcags sgrog 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK013(pa)009:741: h'u big+nana ta kri ta phata /
NK013(pa)009:742: byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)009:743: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:744: dril bu ma ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK013(pa)009:745: khro bo bzhi ka'ang g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad cing /
NK013(pa)009:746: yum rnams g.yon pas dung khrag stobs pa'i tshul can
NK013(pa)009:747: thams cad kyang khro zhing gtum la rnam par 'gyur
NK013(pa)009:748: ba'i zhal can / gar gyis nyams dgus sgeg cing /
NK013(pa)009:749: dur khrod rol pa'i chas kyis brgyan te /
NK013(pa)009:750: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na gdug pa can tshar gcod pa'i tshur gyis bzhugs pa /
NK013(pa)009:751: de ltar rten dang brten par bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)009:752: thams cad kyang me long nang gi gzugs brnyan nam
NK013(pa)009:753: chu nang gi zla ba ltar snang stong sgyu 'phrul
NK013(pa)009:754: d+r+wa ba'i ye shes kyi 'khor lor bzhugs pa'o //
NK013(pa)009:755: gnyis pa ni de la gzhan dbang gis rgyas 'debs
NK013(pa)009:756: dag chen ye shes kyi chus dbang bskur ba ni
NK013(pa)009:757: / gdan gsum rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi srog gi gor /
NK013(pa)009:758: rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan dang phyag mtshan
NK013(pa)009:759: spangs pa re re'i thugs kar rang rang gi phyag
NK013(pa)009:760: mtshan sa bon sngags phreng dang bcas pa las 'od
NK013(pa)009:761: zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs
NK013(pa)009:762: pa thams cad dbang gi lha rigs lnga stangs dpyal
NK013(pa)009:763: gyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzah sa spyan drangs
NK013(pa)009:764: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu
NK013(pa)009:765: r+aa ga na badz+ra swam b+ha wa +aat+ma ko&a hamh
NK013(pa)009:766: zhes bskul bas rjes chags zhu bde'i chu rgyun gyis
NK013(pa)009:767: / dbang bskur / phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK013(pa)009:768: nyon mongs pa ye shes lnga /
NK013(pa)009:770: skye mched sems dpa' sems ma /
NK013(pa)009:771: las dbang khro bo khro mor gnas 'gyur /
NK013(pa)009:772: chu'i lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK013(pa)009:773: pa las rang rigs gtso bor gyur pa'i rigs lnga
NK013(pa)009:774: / sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:775: ces brjod la so so'i dbang rgya dbang sngags bstun zhing /
NK013(pa)009:776: de yang mi bskyod pa la mtshon na /
NK013(pa)009:777: rdo rje phyi sdams las gung mo gnyis brkyang ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK013(pa)009:778: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aadz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa
NK013(pa)009:779: +aat+ma ko & hamh phyag rgya de las mdzub mo
NK013(pa)009:780: gnyis brkyang pa dpral bar bzhag la /
NK013(pa)009:781: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa
NK013(pa)009:782: +aat+ma ko&a hamh srin lag brkyang ba rna ltag g.yas
NK013(pa)009:783: par bzhag la / ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa
NK013(pa)009:784: na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a hamh mthe bong
NK013(pa)009:785: brkyang ba ltag par bzhag la /
NK013(pa)009:786: ma h+aa p+r+aa t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa
NK013(pa)009:787: b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a hamh mathe'u chung brkyang ba rna
NK013(pa)009:789: ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa
NK013(pa)009:790: b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a hamh dkyil 'khor bdag po stangs
NK013(pa)009:791: dpyal dang // bya byed yab yum thub drug la //
NK013(pa)009:792: mi bskyod dbus na bzhugs pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:793: rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan gyur //
NK013(pa)009:794: des mtshon nas rigs gzhan bzhi la'ang rigs gang yin
NK013(pa)009:795: de'i sngags dang po dang phyag rgya dbus su 'jog
NK013(pa)009:796: la / gang dbus su song ba'i shul du mi bskyod pa 'jog pa la /
NK013(pa)009:797: rnam snang gi dbang rgya mdzub mo brkyang pa dang
NK013(pa)009:798: +aa dar+sha dang por brjod pa'i lnga tshan lnga'i sngags
NK013(pa)009:799: rgya'i mthar / rnam snang sa snying byams pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:800: gshin rje yum dang bcas pa la //
NK013(pa)009:801: rnam mdzad dbus na bzhugs pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:802: rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan gyur //
NK013(pa)009:803: rin 'byung gi dbang rgya srin lag brkyang ba dang
NK013(pa)009:804: sa ma t+aa thog mar brjod pa'i lnga tshan lnga'i
NK013(pa)009:805: mthar / rin 'byung nam snying sgrib sel dang //
NK013(pa)009:806: stobs chen yum dang bcas pa la //
NK013(pa)009:807: rin 'byung dbus na bzhugs pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:808: rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan gyur //
NK013(pa)009:809: snang mtha'i dbang rgya mthe bong brkyang pa dang /
NK013(pa)009:810: p+r+aat+ya dang por brjod pa'i lnga tshan lnga'i mthar /
NK013(pa)009:811: snang ba mtha' yas spyan ras gzigs //
NK013(pa)009:812: kun bzang rta mgrin yab yum la //
NK013(pa)009:813: snang mtha' dbus su bzhugs pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:814: rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan gyur //
NK013(pa)009:815: don grub kyi dbang rgya mathe'u chung brkyang pa dang /
NK013(pa)009:816: kri t+ya dang por brjod pa'i lnga tshan lnga'i mthar /
NK013(pa)009:817: don yod grub pa phyag rdor dang /
NK013(pa)009:820: don grub bdag por gyur pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:821: rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan gyur //
NK013(pa)009:822: gsum pa yongs grub rdo rje gsum du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:823: lha thams cad kyi spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK013(pa)009:824: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK013(pa)009:825: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon nas la thim /
NK013(pa)009:826: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:827: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:828: rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor gtugs la /
NK013(pa)009:829: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra
NK013(pa)009:830: s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a hamh mgrin par pad+ma la
NK013(pa)009:831: gnas pa'i +aamhdamara po de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin
NK013(pa)009:832: gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs brgyud bskul /
NK013(pa)009:833: gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon nas +aamhl thim /
NK013(pa)009:834: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:835: +aamhyongasa su gyur pa las snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pas rgyas btab par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:836: rdo rje'i phyag rgya mgrin par gtugs la /
NK013(pa)009:837: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aaka badz+ra swa
NK013(pa)009:838: b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a hamh snying gar nyi ma la
NK013(pa)009:840: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul bas /
NK013(pa)009:841: thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon nas h'u la thim /
NK013(pa)009:842: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:843: h'u yongs su gyur pa las mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyas btab par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:844: rdo rje'i phyag rgya snying gar gtugs la /
NK013(pa)009:845: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa
NK013(pa)009:846: b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a hamh gsum pa phrin las bya
NK013(pa)009:847: ba'i yan lag la drug ste /
NK013(pa)009:848: bsam gtan gyi ngang nas ye shes pa spyan drang ba /
NK013(pa)009:849: sbyin pa'i rang bzhin mchod pa 'bul ba /
NK013(pa)009:850: bzod pa'i ngo bo bshags pa bya ba /
NK013(pa)009:851: brtson 'grus kyi bdag nyid dngos grub bskul ba /
NK013(pa)009:852: tshul khrims kyi ngo bo dam bca' ba /
NK013(pa)009:853: shes rab kyi rang bzhin bzlas pa bya ba dang drug gi /
NK013(pa)009:855: dang po rdo rje'i glus bskul ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:856: rgyal ba rnams kyi ye shes stong nyid bcu drug
NK013(pa)009:857: gi bdag nyid rang bzhin dang ngo bo nyid med
NK013(pa)009:858: pa dang / yod med kyi mtha' gzhig pa'i rnal 'byor gyi don dran par byed pa ste /
NK013(pa)009:859: h'u stong pa shin tu yod med rnal 'byor mthus //
NK013(pa)009:860: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gnas //
NK013(pa)009:861: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs mdzad dgongs su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:862: rdo rje sems dpa' khyood bdag skal bzang dpal /
NK013(pa)009:864: lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis bskul bas /
NK013(pa)009:865: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
NK013(pa)009:867: smon pa med pa ste rang bzhin gyi gnas nas
NK013(pa)009:868: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba rab 'byams ma lus
NK013(pa)009:869: shing lus pa med pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i gdan
NK013(pa)009:870: gsum gyi 'khor lor sad par bsams la spos rol
NK013(pa)009:871: dang bcas / phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK013(pa)009:872: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK013(pa)009:873: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK013(pa)009:874: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la /
NK013(pa)009:876: / 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor ba //
NK013(pa)009:877: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:878: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK013(pa)009:879: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK013(pa)009:880: e h+ye he b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK013(pa)009:881: ni ka dri sh+ya hoh dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes dam
NK013(pa)009:884: rig pa bde gshegs snying po'i me tog phung khams
NK013(pa)009:885: tshogs brgyad dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor dag pa'i dbyings
NK013(pa)009:886: su dor bas rang bzhin dbyer med du 'dres par
NK013(pa)009:887: bsams la / badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK013(pa)009:888: +aamhbadz+ra sa ma ya +aamh h'u badz+ra sa ma ya h'u /
NK013(pa)009:889: swa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK013(pa)009:890: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:891: zhes pas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK013(pa)009:892: ting 'dzin sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis so so'i sku
NK013(pa)009:893: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnams kyi dam tshig
NK013(pa)009:894: gi ngo bo grub par bsams la /
NK013(pa)009:895: dngos grub kyi don du gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:896: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)009:897: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK013(pa)009:898: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)009:899: phyag rgya chen po bdag sbyor cig /
NK013(pa)009:900: ces pas lha rnams dngos grub stsol ba la phyogs pa dang /
NK013(pa)009:901: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u gis ye shes pa dam
NK013(pa)009:902: tshig pa la chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin dbyer
NK013(pa)009:903: med du thim / badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+aam gyis
NK013(pa)009:904: rang nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor du 'tshang ma rgyas
NK013(pa)009:905: kyi bar du brten par bzhugs par bsam /
NK013(pa)009:906: badz+ra sa ma ya ho sa dbang du gyur cing
NK013(pa)009:907: dgyes par bsam dzahmh'u bam hohs brtan zhing gsal bar
NK013(pa)009:908: byas nas / rin chen seng ge'i gdan la yang dag nges bzhugs shing //
NK013(pa)009:909: rang gi lha mo dag dang sras dang g.yog 'khor bcas pa rnams //
NK013(pa)009:910: kun tu bzang po'i smon lam rjes su dgongs mdzad de /
NK013(pa)009:912: / 'jig rten lha dang bcas pa rnams la phan phyir bzhugs su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:915: gnyis pa phyag dang mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:917: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK013(pa)009:918: ji ltar mar la mar bzhag bzhin //
NK013(pa)009:919: rang gis rang gi ye shes gang //
NK013(pa)009:921: zhes pa ltar chos nyid mngon du mthong ba rnams la bya byed kyi gnyis rtog mi dgos kyang /
NK013(pa)009:922: dang po'i blo can rnams ni rang nyid dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)009:923: gyi gtso bo las mar me gcig las gnyis mched
NK013(pa)009:924: kyi tshul du rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gcig phyag
NK013(pa)009:925: gnyis pa'i rnam pas thon nas dkyil 'khor gyi shar
NK013(pa)009:926: sgor 'khod de / sems can thams cad da nga
NK013(pa)009:927: bya byed thun mong bar gyur nas phyag dang mchod
NK013(pa)009:928: pa la sogs pa las kyi rim pa la 'jug
NK013(pa)009:929: sgor 'khod de / par mos pa'o // de'i dang po phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:930: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK013(pa)009:931: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK013(pa)009:932: thugs rje bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK013(pa)009:933: rdo rje sems dpa' che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:934: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas lhun grub pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:935: bya ba byed dang yid chos rnam par dag /
NK013(pa)009:936: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:937: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK013(pa)009:938: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK013(pa)009:939: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:940: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:941: ngo mtshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK013(pa)009:942: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad bskyed mdzad ma //
NK013(pa)009:943: rigs kyi yum gyur rnams la phyag mtshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:944: rnam shes dbang po dag pa'i sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)009:945: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi sras mchog ste //
NK013(pa)009:946: sems dpa' chen po brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:947: sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar ma //
NK013(pa)009:948: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i mchod pas rgyal ba mchod //
NK013(pa)009:949: byang chub lha mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:950: bdug pa me tog mar me dri chab ma //
NK013(pa)009:951: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la mchod 'bul ma //
NK013(pa)009:952: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:953: drag shul thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)009:954: tshad med bzhi ldan sgo bzhi thub par bsrung //
NK013(pa)009:955: mthar byed sgo ba bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:956: rtag chad lta 'byin gsang ba yum gyi ngang //
NK013(pa)009:957: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrogs dril 'khrol ma //
NK013(pa)009:958: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:959: steng 'og phyogs bzhir 'jig rten gdul ba'i gtso //
NK013(pa)009:960: nyon mongs drug 'joms rgyud drug dag par sbyang //
NK013(pa)009:961: bcom ldan thub pa drug la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:962: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:963: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:964: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:965: mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:966: mngon par byang chub sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:967: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyis bsgrubs pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:968: tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing yon tan mthar phyin pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:969: sku dang ye shes tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:970: a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh zhes phyag bya'o //
NK013(pa)009:971: gnyis pa mchod pa la bcu gsum las /
NK013(pa)009:972: dang po phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:973: sngags bla med spyi'i grub mtha'i mngon rtogs phyag rgya'i khong nas 'don pa las /
NK013(pa)009:976: sa bon chos rgya bca' ba dam rgya /
NK013(pa)009:977: dgrol ba las rgya'i don nges pas /
NK013(pa)009:978: lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la /
NK013(pa)009:981: gung mdzub srin lag mthe bong mathe'u chung rnams la /
NK013(pa)009:983: g.yon gyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la /
NK013(pa)009:988: rnams kyis mtshan par bsam la /
NK013(pa)009:989: h'u sgyu 'phrul dra ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:990: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK013(pa)009:991: gsang ba de nyid nges pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:993: mi bskyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK013(pa)009:994: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge //
NK013(pa)009:995: lnga gnyis zung du sprad pa las /
NK013(pa)009:998: sbyar bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK013(pa)009:999: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK013(pa)009:1000: g.yas kyi mdzub mo dang g.yon gyi gung mo /
NK013(pa)009:1001: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK013(pa)009:1002: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK013(pa)009:1003: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //
NK013(pa)009:1006: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1008: h'u sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1009: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1011: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bsten //
NK013(pa)009:1014: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1016: m+aum sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1020: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK013(pa)009:1023: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1025: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1027: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bsten //
NK013(pa)009:1029: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1030: l+aam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1032: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK013(pa)009:1034: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1035: s+w+aa sgreng rtse mor rin chen 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1036: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1038: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bsten //
NK013(pa)009:1040: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1041: m+aam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1043: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK013(pa)009:1045: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan /
NK013(pa)009:1048: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1050: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bsten /
NK013(pa)009:1053: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1054: p+aam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1056: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK013(pa)009:1058: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1059: h+aa sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1060: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1062: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bsten //
NK013(pa)009:1064: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)009:1065: tam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)009:1067: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK013(pa)009:1069: h'u sogs bsgreng rgya g.yas g.yon so so'i gung mdzub nas re mos kho nar bsgreng ba'o /
NK013(pa)009:1071: / 'di ni rgyal ba thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)009:1072: dgyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:1073: phyag rgya'i mchod pa chen po yin //
NK013(pa)009:1074: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK013(pa)009:1075: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1076: ces rim pa bzhin rigs lnga so so'i phyag rgya bca' ba ste /
NK013(pa)009:1077: de yang phyag rgya mdun du bsgyur nas yab g.yon dang /
NK013(pa)009:1081: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)009:1082: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK013(pa)009:1083: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK013(pa)009:1084: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK013(pa)009:1085: na mas+sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK013(pa)009:1086: khe b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam
NK013(pa)009:1087: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:1088: zhes phyi nang gsang ba'i 'dod yon gyi dngos po
NK013(pa)009:1089: mtha' dag spyod yul yongs su dag pa kun tu
NK013(pa)009:1090: bzang po'i mchod sprin chen por 'bul lo //
NK013(pa)009:1092: yang dag don du dag mod kyang /
NK013(pa)009:1094: / 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK013(pa)009:1095: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil nas kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1096: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1097: a ha ra a ha ra sarba bid+ya d+ha ra
NK013(pa)009:1098: p+au dzi te na mas+sa man+ta bud+d+ha nam ga ga
NK013(pa)009:1099: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:1100: zhes phyag zhabs la nye reg dang mchod yon du dbul lo //
NK013(pa)009:1102: so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK013(pa)009:1103: h'u spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa ma //
NK013(pa)009:1105: byams pa thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1106: badz+ra d+h+au pe'i mchod par rol /
NK013(pa)009:1107: pa na peem pe nu su ra to /
NK013(pa)009:1109: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK013(pa)009:1111: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK013(pa)009:1112: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+hu pe d+hu /
NK013(pa)009:1115: snying rje thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1116: badz+ra pu sh+pe'i mchod par rol /
NK013(pa)009:1118: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK013(pa)009:1119: dbang gi phyag na sgron ma bsnams //
NK013(pa)009:1121: dga' ba thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1122: badz+ra lo ke'i mchod par rol //
NK013(pa)009:1124: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+aih tsan+da bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs ma //
NK013(pa)009:1126: btang snyoms thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1129: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK013(pa)009:1130: lha mo rnams kyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs mchod
NK013(pa)009:1131: nas shangs la sogs pa'i dbang po'i sgo so so
NK013(pa)009:1133: +aahmh'u rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)009:1134: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1135: mchod chen thams cad dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1138: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK013(pa)009:1139: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK013(pa)009:1140: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK013(pa)009:1141: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK013(pa)009:1142: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK013(pa)009:1143: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba //
NK013(pa)009:1144: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi sman //
NK013(pa)009:1145: thams cad bdud rtsi'i rnal 'byor che //
NK013(pa)009:1146: byang chub sems ni rdo rje ste //
NK013(pa)009:1147: sha chen mchod pa rin po che //
NK013(pa)009:1148: pad+ma me tog yang dag ldan //
NK013(pa)009:1149: rdo rje chu ste las kyi mchog /
NK013(pa)009:1150: zas mchog tshe yi dri chen po //
NK013(pa)009:1151: ga bur shel gyi pog por dri //
NK013(pa)009:1152: rin chen me ltar 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)009:1153: ma lus 'dus pa'i thig le che //
NK013(pa)009:1154: gcig tu dpa' bo'i ro rnams dang //
NK013(pa)009:1155: gnyis su med par mnyam sbyar nas //
NK013(pa)009:1156: bdud rtsi dam pa rin chen bcud //
NK013(pa)009:1157: bde gshegs rnams kyi thugs dam nyid //
NK013(pa)009:1158: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i dngos grub mchog /
NK013(pa)009:1160: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK013(pa)009:1161: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1162: bzhes nas kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK013(pa)009:1163: bla med dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1164: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK013(pa)009:1166: bye brag tu dkon mchog 'grel las /
NK013(pa)009:1167: dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin byang chub sems //
NK013(pa)009:1168: de stsol bla ma de rgya lhag pa'i lha //
NK013(pa)009:1169: de dbang sprul pa'i 'khor lor bcas pa la //
NK013(pa)009:1170: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)009:1171: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK013(pa)009:1173: kun bzang rigs lnga rigs gsum dra ma lnga //
NK013(pa)009:1174: lung bstan rdo rje u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK013(pa)009:1175: drang srong b+ha shi pra b+ha ha sti la //
NK013(pa)009:1176: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)009:1178: rgyal dbang pad+ma k+aa ra gnyags lo dang //
NK013(pa)009:1179: sog po lha dpal gnubs chen sras slob brgyud //
NK013(pa)009:1180: shes rab mchog dang ye shes 'byung gnas la //
NK013(pa)009:1183: grub thob zur chen zur chung ka chen bzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1184: gsang bdag sgro phug pan chen rong pa'i zhabs //
NK013(pa)009:1188: purnee d+ha dza chos seng bud+d+ha sh+r+ai /
NK013(pa)009:1189: bsod nams mgon po sgrol chen dge rong pas dgung
NK013(pa)009:1190: lo brgya dang nyi shu skor bzhugs shing rnam thar
NK013(pa)009:1191: na mdo ston sed+ge las gsan tshul yod pa sgro
NK013(pa)009:1194: sh+aakya bshes gnyen bra bo chos 'bum la //
NK013(pa)009:1197: rat+na b+ha dra rdo rje dpal bzang po //
NK013(pa)009:1198: dan 'bag gzhon nu kun mkhyen dri med 'od //
NK013(pa)009:1199: gtad rgya lung rdzogs 'jigs med gling pa la //
NK013(pa)009:1202: phung khams dag pa'i gshegs pa gshegs ma dang //
NK013(pa)009:1203: dbang yul dag pa'i byang chub lcam dral tshogs //
NK013(pa)009:1204: las la dbang ba'i sgo skyong thub drugs la //
NK013(pa)009:1207: mdor na rab 'byams dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK013(pa)009:1208: gnas yul d+aak+ki dam can chos skyong dang //
NK013(pa)009:1209: zhing skyong gzhi bdag dkar phyogs skyong ba'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)009:1210: dus gsum pha ma 'gro ba rigs drug la //
NK013(pa)009:1211: sman mchod 'bul lo mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK013(pa)009:1212: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK013(pa)009:1213: zhes guh+ya lag gi phyag rgyas gtor bas /
NK013(pa)009:1214: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i zegs ma mkha' la sprin
NK013(pa)009:1215: bzhin du chags pa las bdud rtsi'i char chen po
NK013(pa)009:1216: babs te lha tshogs thams cad mnyes zheng tshim par
NK013(pa)009:1217: bsam la / mthar dongs grub blang ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1218: rang gi lce la h'u yig dang /
NK013(pa)009:1219: sman gyi steng du +aahmh'u gsum bsgom ste /
NK013(pa)009:1220: +aahmh'uh rdo rje lce yi dam tshig la //
NK013(pa)009:1221: rdo rje can gyi 'bru gsum sgom //
NK013(pa)009:1222: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NK013(pa)009:1223: myangs na dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)009:1224: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK013(pa)009:1225: w+aaka sid+d+hi ah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK013(pa)009:1226: zhes rim par bardzoda cing blangs nas lce la bzhag
NK013(pa)009:1227: pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam
NK013(pa)009:1228: mo // drug pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1229: 'dod yon gyi lha mo dpag tu med pas dkyil
NK013(pa)009:1230: 'khor ba rnams dgyes pa bskyed nas rang la gnyis
NK013(pa)009:1231: med du gyur par bsam zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1232: h'uh bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK013(pa)009:1233: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro /
NK013(pa)009:1235: / 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK013(pa)009:1236: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1237: +aahmh'u su ra to u pa b+h+yah ka ma la
NK013(pa)009:1238: m+aa la badz+ra a mri ta ha ra na pra
NK013(pa)009:1239: t+aits+tsha b+ha ga w+aan dzahmh'u bam hoh a la la
NK013(pa)009:1240: hoh zhes dang / pa na pem sogs bzhi bsnol gyis kyang mchod do //
NK013(pa)009:1241: bdun pa bdud rtsi gsang nan gyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1242: bdud rtsi bzed zhal du lan gsum 'phyar zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1243: +aahh+aum mi bskyod ye shes bde ba'i mchog dang ldan pa'i ro la bsnam du gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1245: byang chub sems pa'i bde mchog de nyid 'gog pa rnams las bslang ba'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:1246: chags pa med pa'i bde mchog kun tu myong mdzad bzhes shing bsnam du gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1248: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde la rol zhing dam bcas 'jig rten sgrol //
NK013(pa)009:1249: byang chub skye gnas bde mchog dbyings las mi nyams bde ba'i gar mdzod cig /
NK013(pa)009:1251: zhen cing chags pa'i mtha' la nyon mongs rno brkam gzir ba yi //
NK013(pa)009:1252: myong byed bde mchog brgyad dang ldan pas thabs kyi sku la smre bar mdzod /
NK013(pa)009:1254: / 'gro kun tshangs par spyod pa'i byang chub bsgo mor lam ston cig /
NK013(pa)009:1255: bde mchog bdud rtsi khyad par med pa'i tshogs la bka' lcol cig /
NK013(pa)009:1257: zhes dang pos dkyil 'khor pa dgyes pa bskyed /
NK013(pa)009:1258: gnyis pas byang chub sems dpa'i bde mchog ma rtogs pa'i nyan thos rnams 'gog pa las bslang /
NK013(pa)009:1259: gsum pas de gzhin gshegs pa rnams gzhan don la bskul zhing gtor ma la sbran no //
NK013(pa)009:1260: brgyad pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1261: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK013(pa)009:1262: sems kyis yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK013(pa)009:1263: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK013(pa)009:1264: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:1265: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1266: mdzes par bres shing spras pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:1268: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK013(pa)009:1269: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK013(pa)009:1270: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK013(pa)009:1271: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK013(pa)009:1272: bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK013(pa)009:1273: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK013(pa)009:1274: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK013(pa)009:1275: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK013(pa)009:1276: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK013(pa)009:1277: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK013(pa)009:1278: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK013(pa)009:1280: skal ldan gsal pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK013(pa)009:1281: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK013(pa)009:1282: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK013(pa)009:1283: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por sgom //
NK013(pa)009:1285: rang gi thugs ka nas ram dpag tu med pa chad /
NK013(pa)009:1287: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas sems can
NK013(pa)009:1288: thams cad kyi snying nang na gnas pa'i rigs drug
NK013(pa)009:1289: gi sa bon bag chags dang bcas par bsregs /
NK013(pa)009:1290: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bsam zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1292: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK013(pa)009:1293: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK013(pa)009:1294: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK013(pa)009:1295: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK013(pa)009:1297: yab kyi nor bu h'u las rtse lnga pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:1298: rdo rje'i dbyibs can zla bar gyis mtshan //
NK013(pa)009:1299: yum gyi chos 'byung m+aam las 'dab brgyad kyi //
NK013(pa)009:1300: pad+ma'i ze 'bru nyi mar m+aum gyis mtshan //
NK013(pa)009:1301: yab kyis sa ma ho yi brdas bskul bas //
NK013(pa)009:1302: yum gyis sa ma ya s+t+wam lan btab pa //
NK013(pa)009:1303: yab kyis r+aa ga ya ho'i brda sbyar bas //
NK013(pa)009:1304: yum gyis r+aa ga ya mi'i brda yis bskul //
NK013(pa)009:1305: dzahmh'u bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha ho /
NK013(pa)009:1306: zhes dga' ba bzhi'i rol mo so sor rtog pa'ii ye shes su sad par bsam la /
NK013(pa)009:1308: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)009:1309: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK013(pa)009:1310: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK013(pa)009:1311: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK013(pa)009:1312: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)009:1313: zhes pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rjes
NK013(pa)009:1314: su chags pa dang dbyer med pa'i nga rgyal bya'o
NK013(pa)009:1315: // bcu gcig pa 'dod yon ro mnyam gyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1316: h'u bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo /
NK013(pa)009:1317: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni /
NK013(pa)009:1319: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol /
NK013(pa)009:1321: / 'dod yon gyi snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mor dag pa dang /
NK013(pa)009:1322: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad bde ba chen por
NK013(pa)009:1323: ro gcig tu gyur par bsam pa ni bla na
NK013(pa)009:1324: med pa'i dug gsum lam du slong ba'i mchod pa'o
NK013(pa)009:1325: // bcu gnyis pa rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1326: dbang po'i spyod yul rang bzhin dngos po med //
NK013(pa)009:1327: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin dug lnga sel //
NK013(pa)009:1328: dam rdzas dag pa lnga dang zhal zas lnga //
NK013(pa)009:1329: sku lnga chos lnga rang bzhin dbyer med mnyam //
NK013(pa)009:1330: de phyir dag pas dag pa nyid mchod phyir //
NK013(pa)009:1331: chos nyid la ni chos nyid thim par 'bul //
NK013(pa)009:1332: dri med rnam dag nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK013(pa)009:1333: log rtog mtshan ma mang po'i sprin spungs te //
NK013(pa)009:1334: ye shes nyi ma'i 'od kyis rab brgyan nas //
NK013(pa)009:1335: dag pa'i don phyir rtogs nas mchod par 'bul //
NK013(pa)009:1336: mnyam nyid blang dor med la snyoms par 'jug pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:1337: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yi rgyan /
NK013(pa)009:1339: / 'dod yon lnga yi lha mor byin brlabs pas //
NK013(pa)009:1340: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1341: zhes pa'i rol mo ji snyed pa thams cad kyis
NK013(pa)009:1342: 'khor gsum ye shes su dag par mngon du byas
NK013(pa)009:1343: nas / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)009:1344: zhes mchod pa'i nga rgyal bya zhing rol mo ye shes kyi sgras bskul la /
NK013(pa)009:1345: bcu gsum pa glu ye shes kyi mchod pas bstod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1346: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs dril stabs dang bcas bsor dkrol /
NK013(pa)009:1348: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le pad skor /
NK013(pa)009:1352: snang stong nang skor thar sbyar /
NK013(pa)009:1353: thig le kun tu rdzogs ho //
NK013(pa)009:1354: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK013(pa)009:1355: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK013(pa)009:1356: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK013(pa)009:1357: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che ho //
NK013(pa)009:1358: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK013(pa)009:1359: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK013(pa)009:1360: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK013(pa)009:1361: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che ho //
NK013(pa)009:1362: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)009:1363: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs spro //
NK013(pa)009:1364: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK013(pa)009:1365: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po ho //
NK013(pa)009:1366: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK013(pa)009:1367: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK013(pa)009:1368: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK013(pa)009:1369: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub ho //
NK013(pa)009:1370: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)009:1371: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK013(pa)009:1373: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK013(pa)009:1374: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho //
NK013(pa)009:1375: zhes yon tan rjes su dran pa'i sgo nas chos nyid kyi rang sgras bstod par bya'o //
NK013(pa)009:1376: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1378: spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)009:1379: rnam par dag pa na dus gsum du gshegs shing
NK013(pa)009:1380: bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das /
NK013(pa)009:1381: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi bye
NK013(pa)009:1382: brag dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje
NK013(pa)009:1383: sems dpa' la sogs pa'i rigs lnga'i bde bar gshegs
NK013(pa)009:1384: pa / rigs mchog gzungs kyi yum gyi dbyings na rnam par bzhugs pa sems dpa'i tshogs /
NK013(pa)009:1386: ye shes chen po'i dbang phyug thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid /
NK013(pa)009:1387: sgrol ba'i mkha' 'gro rang bzhin gyi rnal 'byor /
NK013(pa)009:1389: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1390: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK013(pa)009:1391: dang po gsang ba rdo rje theg pa'i sgor khas 'ches te /
NK013(pa)009:1392: dam tshig gnyen po ma nor bar mnos pa las /
NK013(pa)009:1393: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa /
NK013(pa)009:1394: lha nye bar ma bsgom pa /
NK013(pa)009:1395: snyiing po dag par ma bgrangs pa /
NK013(pa)009:1396: sbyor ba mang pos bar bskums pa /
NK013(pa)009:1397: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK013(pa)009:1398: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK013(pa)009:1399: mchod pa lo zla las 'das pa /
NK013(pa)009:1400: dam rdzas lag len rdo ma thogs pa /
NK013(pa)009:1403: ting 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK013(pa)009:1404: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod dam pa klong du ma gyur cing /
NK013(pa)009:1405: sems can gyi spyod pa rang thad du gyur pa dang /
NK013(pa)009:1406: khyad par du sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK013(pa)009:1407: khyad par gyi dam tshig gnyen po mngon par nos pa las /
NK013(pa)009:1408: nyams shing zhig ral du gyur pa ci mchis pa
NK013(pa)009:1409: thams cad shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis
NK013(pa)009:1410: mthol zhing bshags par mchis na /
NK013(pa)009:1411: dbyings nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i ngang gis sku bzod pa chen po dang du bzhes nas /
NK013(pa)009:1412: tshangs pa mchog yid bzhin du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1413: bzhi pa dngos grub gsol ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1414: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK013(pa)009:1416: mngon par shes pa drug rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK013(pa)009:1419: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs kyi bla man chad nas /
NK013(pa)009:1420: dngos grub kyi skal ba dang rigs brgyud gang lags
NK013(pa)009:1421: pa thams cad phyi mar bsdad mi 'tshal bar dus
NK013(pa)009:1422: da lta nyid du thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1423: rnal 'byor pa la bar du gcod par byed pa sdang ba'i dgra /
NK013(pa)009:1430: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang ltas ngan pa /
NK013(pa)009:1431: mi shis pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad phyir bzlog
NK013(pa)009:1432: cing ming yang mi grags pa zhi ba chen po
NK013(pa)009:1433: mdzad du gsol / gal te zhi bas bsgyur du
NK013(pa)009:1434: mi btub pa dag drag po'i phrin las kyi dbang
NK013(pa)009:1437: bsgral zhing sbar ba la sogs te /
NK013(pa)009:1438: phrin las drag thabs rnam pa bzhis /
NK013(pa)009:1439: ji ltar 'dul bar 'tshams pa bzhin mdzad nas ming tsam yang mi grags par mdzad du gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1440: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du zhugs pa rnams //
NK013(pa)009:1441: gcad gtubs sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur yang //
NK013(pa)009:1442: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pa //
NK013(pa)009:1443: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:1444: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi /
NK013(pa)009:1446: / 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'byung ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:1447: lus ngag sems la tshe 'di rdo rje rab snang ste //
NK013(pa)009:1448: re smon thams cad dus 'di nyid du stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1450: lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1451: lhag pa'i bsam pa rtse gcig pas /
NK013(pa)009:1453: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK013(pa)009:1454: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK013(pa)009:1455: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa /
NK013(pa)009:1457: / 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK013(pa)009:1458: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK013(pa)009:1459: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK013(pa)009:1460: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK013(pa)009:1461: rdo rje rgyal pos byin brlab mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1463: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrub //
NK013(pa)009:1464: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK013(pa)009:1466: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK013(pa)009:1471: skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba dang bzhi las /
NK013(pa)009:1473: yang dag don gyi snying po ni //
NK013(pa)009:1474: brjod pa du ma'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1475: gang nas btsal kyang mi rnyed pas //
NK013(pa)009:1476: rang rig dri med dag pa yin //
NK013(pa)009:1477: de la rtag tu mos pa ni //
NK013(pa)009:1478: bsnyen pa'i dam pa mchog yin no //
NK013(pa)009:1479: sems nyid theg par rab nges na //
NK013(pa)009:1481: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pa //
NK013(pa)009:1482: da lta nyid du mngon gyur cig /
NK013(pa)009:1483: ces de kho na nyid kyi don dran par bya'o //
NK013(pa)009:1485: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor legs par gsal btab nas /
NK013(pa)009:1486: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he phatahdzahmh'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa phata
NK013(pa)009:1487: dzah zhes brjod pas dam tshig gi 'khor lo las
NK013(pa)009:1488: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas
NK013(pa)009:1489: pa logs su phye nas mdun gyi nam mkha' me
NK013(pa)009:1490: ri 'dabs 'byar gyi tshul du bzhugs par mos pa'o
NK013(pa)009:1492: bdag mdun gyi lha rnams kyi ye shes sems dpa'
NK013(pa)009:1493: so so'i thugs kar rang rang gi phyag mtshan gyi
NK013(pa)009:1494: lte bar dngas ma'i thugs srog h'u yig la sogs
NK013(pa)009:1495: pa'i mthar bzla bya'i sngags kyi phreng bas bskor bar
NK013(pa)009:1496: gsal btab la / sngags zlos ba'i tshe bdag gi
NK013(pa)009:1497: thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod pa'i tshul
NK013(pa)009:1498: du spros pas ye shes kyi lha tshogs rnams dgyes
NK013(pa)009:1499: gsal btab la / pa bskyed / thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK013(pa)009:1500: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams
NK013(pa)009:1501: cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam pas bdag la
NK013(pa)009:1502: stsal zhing thim par bsam la /
NK013(pa)009:1503: de yang dbang po mchog tu gyur pa rnams kyis dam ye /
NK013(pa)009:1504: 'phro 'du ste gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa'i ngang
NK013(pa)009:1505: nas bdud bzhi bcom pa'i mtshan nyid rig par bya
NK013(pa)009:1506: ste / man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba las /
NK013(pa)009:1507: 'di ltar bsnyen pa'ang byang chub kyi sems shes pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK013(pa)009:1508: ma skyes pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom mo //
NK013(pa)009:1509: nye ba'i bsnyen pa bdag nyid lhar shes pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK013(pa)009:1510: sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis phung po'i bdud bcom mo //
NK013(pa)009:1511: sgrub pa yum bskyed pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK013(pa)009:1512: rdul dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom mo //
NK013(pa)009:1513: sgrub pa chen po thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i mtshan nyid /
NK013(pa)009:1514: mi dmigs mkha' dang mnyam pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK013(pa)009:1515: lha'i bu'i bdud bar chad g.yeng ba'i bdud bcom mo
NK013(pa)009:1516: // de ltar gang la bdud rnam pa bzhi 'dul
NK013(pa)009:1517: bar byed pa'i mthu yod pa'i lam de ni rnam
NK013(pa)009:1518: par dag pa'i lam yin la /
NK013(pa)009:1520: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika m+aum d+h+aa te shwa r+ai /
NK013(pa)009:1530: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+aam /
NK013(pa)009:1532: t+r+aam ma le sa ma ya ho h+r+aim h+aa h'u pad+ma pra da ma /
NK013(pa)009:1533: h+r+aim g+ai ti r+aa ga ham /
NK013(pa)009:1536: mee d+ha ra nee s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:1538: th+l+him ni sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:1540: h'u sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:1541: bam d+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK013(pa)009:1542: m+aum sh+ri am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:1545: mah+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:1547: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:1549: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:1551: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:1553: a a a badz+ri b+hadra sa man+ta a /
NK013(pa)009:1555: mu ne h'u trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)009:1560: zhes pa rnams rim pa bzhin gtso 'khor gyi 'gros dang sbyar nas bazla'o //
NK013(pa)009:1561: bzhi pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba la /
NK013(pa)009:1564: ye shes pa bsdu ba dang gsum /
NK013(pa)009:1566: dril stabs dang bcas rdo rje gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1567: h'u rnam shes rnam dag bcom dril stabs dang bcas rdo rje gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1569: zhe sdang rnam dag chos dbyings pad skor /
NK013(pa)009:1571: mthing ga rdo rje gtod de dril bu dkur brten /
NK013(pa)009:1573: phyag na rdo rje 'bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)009:1574: thugs mchog rdo rje sems la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)009:1575: gzugs phung rnam dag bcom ldan rnam snang mdzad //
NK013(pa)009:1576: gti mug rnam dag me long ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)009:1577: dung mdog phyag na 'khor rang gi rgya stabs /
NK013(pa)009:1579: sku mchog rnam snang mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)009:1580: tshor ba rnam dag bcom ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK013(pa)009:1581: nga rgyal rnam dag mnyam nyid ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)009:1582: gser mdog phyag na rin chen 'bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)009:1583: yon tan rin chen 'byung la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK013(pa)009:1585: / 'du shes rnam dag bcom ldan snang mtha' yas /
NK013(pa)009:1587: / 'dod chags rnam dag kun rtog ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)009:1588: le brgan phyag na pad+ma 'bar ba bsnam //
NK013(pa)009:1589: gsung mchog snang mtha' yas la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK013(pa)009:1591: / 'du byed rnam dag bcom ldan don yod grub //
NK013(pa)009:1592: phrag dog rnam dag bya grub ye shes ngang //
NK013(pa)009:1593: ljang gu phyag na ral gri 'bar ba bsnams //
NK013(pa)009:1594: phrin las don yod grub la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK013(pa)009:1596: / 'byung ba rnam dag rigs kyi yum chen lnga //
NK013(pa)009:1597: kun bzang spyan ma m+aa ma gos dkar sgrol //
NK013(pa)009:1598: thabs kyi sku la shes rab dgyes khyud rgya /
NK013(pa)009:1600: rigs kyi yum chen lnga la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)009:1602: bskal bzang byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams ni //
NK013(pa)009:1603: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi sras pad skor /
NK013(pa)009:1606: yon tan mi zad sprul pa bsam yas pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:1608: sems dpa' chen po brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)009:1610: sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar can //
NK013(pa)009:1611: bdug pa me tog mar me rang rang gi phyag rgya /
NK013(pa)009:1613: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams pad skor /
NK013(pa)009:1615: mchod pa'i lha mo thal sbyar /
NK013(pa)009:1617: ye shes sgo ba chen po yab yum brgyad //
NK013(pa)009:1618: gshin rje stobs chen rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK013(pa)009:1619: lcags kyu rang rang phyag rgya /
NK013(pa)009:1620: zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma //
NK013(pa)009:1621: sgo ba yab yum brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)009:1622: chos nyid stong pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1623: chos nyid kun tu bzang po 'du 'bral med //
NK013(pa)009:1624: chos nyid khyab gdal mnyam gzhag chen po'i ye shes kyi //
NK013(pa)009:1625: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK013(pa)009:1626: ye shes bzhii la rigs bzhi'i phrin las kyis /
NK013(pa)009:1628: / 'jig rten drug gi bye ba phrag brgya ru //
NK013(pa)009:1630: pa bye ba phrag brgyas 'gro drug gi //
NK013(pa)009:1631: don mdzad thub pa drug la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK013(pa)009:1634: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NK013(pa)009:1635: che ba'i yon tan brjod kyis mi lang yang //
NK013(pa)009:1636: yon tan cha shas brjod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK013(pa)009:1637: rig 'dzin sngags 'chang rnal 'byor bdag cag gi //
NK013(pa)009:1638: las dang nyon mongs bag chags gtan spyangs nas //
NK013(pa)009:1639: tshe 'di nyid la rig 'dzin mchog thob ste //
NK013(pa)009:1640: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas thob shog /
NK013(pa)009:1643: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK013(pa)009:1644: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK013(pa)009:1645: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bo smin //
NK013(pa)009:1646: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK013(pa)009:1647: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK013(pa)009:1648: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur par //
