NK013(pa)009:1649: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK013(pa)009:1650: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1651: zhes bzlas pa'i nyes byas su gyur pa thams cad bshags shing dag par bya'o //
NK013(pa)009:1653: rang bzhin dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis rang bzhin dbyer med du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)009:1654: badz+ra sa ma ya sogs lnga dang /
NK013(pa)009:1655: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs sogs kyis rig
NK013(pa)009:1656: pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul nas badz+ra
NK013(pa)009:1657: sa ma ya h'u zhes brjod pas ye shes kyi
NK013(pa)009:1658: 'khor lo dam tshig pa la chu la chu bzhag
NK013(pa)009:1659: pa bzhin dbyer med du thim /
NK013(pa)009:1662: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh zhes dbang du sgyur nas dgyes shing chags par byas /
NK013(pa)009:1663: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis brtan cing gsal bar byas nas yi ge brgya pa yang bazla'o //
NK013(pa)009:1664: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la tshogs kyi mchod pa /
NK013(pa)009:1667: go bgo lus bsrung dang bzhi ste /
NK013(pa)009:1668: dang po tshogs mchod la lnga las /
NK013(pa)009:1669: dang po bshams shing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1670: dza gad dang m+aam sa gtso bor gyur pa'i yo byad ci 'byor pa bshams nas /
NK013(pa)009:1672: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sarba dra byam sho d+ha ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:1674: ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus te stong par sbyangs /
NK013(pa)009:1676: zhal zas kyi snod du nyi ma la h'u s+w+aa
NK013(pa)009:1677: +aam h+aa las bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes
NK013(pa)009:1678: lnga'i rang bzhin bdud rtsi ro brgya pa 'dod yon
NK013(pa)009:1679: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa so so'i
NK013(pa)009:1680: lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK013(pa)009:1681: bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar bsam la yi ge gsum
NK013(pa)009:1682: lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK013(pa)009:1683: gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan 'dren ni /
NK013(pa)009:1684: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK013(pa)009:1685: rang rigs mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK013(pa)009:1687: tshogs mchog dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1688: e h+ye hi sogs kyis tshogs zhing mkha' khyab tu sad par bya /
NK013(pa)009:1689: gsum pa mchod pa la gnyis kyi /
NK013(pa)009:1690: dang po ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1692: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa mo //
NK013(pa)009:1694: byams pa thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1695: badz+ra d+hu pe'i mchod par rol /
NK013(pa)009:1696: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+hu pe d+hu //
NK013(pa)009:1699: snying rje thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1701: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu //
NK013(pa)009:1702: dbang gi phyag na sgron ma bsnams //
NK013(pa)009:1704: dga' ba thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1705: badz+ra lo ke'i mchod par rol //
NK013(pa)009:1706: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+aih tsan+dana bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs ma //
NK013(pa)009:1708: btang snyoms thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)009:1710: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK013(pa)009:1712: h'u rdo rje sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK013(pa)009:1713: sems dpa' sngon po'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK013(pa)009:1714: me long lta bu'i ye shes las //
NK013(pa)009:1715: badz+ra l+aa s+ye'i mchod par rol //
NK013(pa)009:1716: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga l+aa s+ye'i h'u //
NK013(pa)009:1720: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las //
NK013(pa)009:1721: badz+ra m+aa le'i mchod par rol //
NK013(pa)009:1722: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga m+aa le t+r+aam /
NK013(pa)009:1723: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK013(pa)009:1724: sbyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK013(pa)009:1725: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes las //
NK013(pa)009:1727: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga girti h+r+aih gar mkhan 'gying bag gzir ldan ma //
NK013(pa)009:1729: bya ba nan tan ye shes las //
NK013(pa)009:1731: badz+ra r+aa ga nirti ah gnyis pa tshogs rdzas kyi mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1732: zhal zas kyi phud rim par spros la /
NK013(pa)009:1734: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur cing //
NK013(pa)009:1735: byang chub sems dang ma chags pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:1736: gnyis su med par thim gyur nas //
NK013(pa)009:1737: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par rol /
NK013(pa)009:1739: / 'dod yon lnga po thams cad dang //
NK013(pa)009:1740: sna tshogs snang ba thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)009:1741: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK013(pa)009:1742: gzugs mdzes lha dang lha mor brtag /
NK013(pa)009:1743: sna tshogs gzugs ni thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)009:1744: snang stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1745: chos dbyings dag pa'i ye shes ste //
NK013(pa)009:1746: rdo rje lha mo gzugs mdzes ma //
NK013(pa)009:1747: thams cad ma lus sgra rnams ni //
NK013(pa)009:1748: grag stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1749: me long lta bu'i ye shes te //
NK013(pa)009:1750: rdo rje lha mo 'jam pa'i sgra //
NK013(pa)009:1751: bde ba tshim byed bsod nams te //
NK013(pa)009:1752: tshim stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1753: brjod med mi gnas ye shes te //
NK013(pa)009:1754: rdo rje chags med pad+ma'i gsung //
NK013(pa)009:1755: bde gshegs dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK013(pa)009:1756: bde ba ro yis tshim byed pa //
NK013(pa)009:1757: ro stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1758: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes te //
NK013(pa)009:1759: thams cad tshim byed ro yi lha //
NK013(pa)009:1760: rdo rje reg bya myong byed ma //
NK013(pa)009:1761: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)009:1762: bde mchog dkyil 'khor yang byed ma //
NK013(pa)009:1763: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te //
NK013(pa)009:1764: rdo rje reg bya'i lha mo rnams /
NK013(pa)009:1766: / 'dod yon phyag na snams nas ni //
NK013(pa)009:1767: rkang pas stabs byed lag gar bsgyur //
NK013(pa)009:1768: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs blang nas ni //
NK013(pa)009:1770: ho bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor kyi lha tshogs
NK013(pa)009:1771: rnams la tshogs kyi mchod pa chen po 'bul zhing
NK013(pa)009:1772: mchis na / sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes shing tshims nas /
NK013(pa)009:1773: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad bskangs te bla na med pa'i dngos grub thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK013(pa)009:1774: bzhi pa tshogs la rol ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1775: las kyi rdo rjes 'khor lo 'dus pa'i gtso bo la phyag byas /
NK013(pa)009:1776: thabs shes kyi rdzas bsnol mar 'bul zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1777: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas dpal //
NK013(pa)009:1778: log rtog mtshan ma'i spros pa ngang gis zhi //
NK013(pa)009:1779: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder spyad nas kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1780: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1781: zhes stob des kyang pad+ma'i phyag rgya bskor zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1784: ho bdag lus phung khams skye mched ni //
NK013(pa)009:1785: gdan gsum tshang ba'i ngo bo ste //
NK013(pa)009:1786: dam pa rigs rgya'i dkyil 'khor lha //
NK013(pa)009:1787: bsgul bskyod thams cad bde ba che //
NK013(pa)009:1788: rdo rje'i dam tshig bla na med //
NK013(pa)009:1789: gnyis med mnyam pa'i ngang du rol //
NK013(pa)009:1790: rnal 'byor lam gyi tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK013(pa)009:1791: zas kyis sgrib par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK013(pa)009:1792: gtan pa med pa'i sbyin bdag kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1793: theg chen 'bras bur spyod par shog /
NK013(pa)009:1795: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK013(pa)009:1796: dral rnams kyis dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro
NK013(pa)009:1797: ba ma lus pa dbang du 'du bar gyur cig
NK013(pa)009:1798: / ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen por gyur cig /
NK013(pa)009:1799: rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang dpe byad la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK013(pa)009:1800: zhal zas kyi bye brag mang po gsol bas zhi
NK013(pa)009:1801: khro'i phrin las kyi rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs la dbang
NK013(pa)009:1804: lnga pa lhag ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1805: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog med par bsdus /
NK013(pa)009:1806: lha mchod pa'i lhag mas bsnan pa dkyil 'khor dang
NK013(pa)009:1807: ha cang mi nye ba'i shar lhor dri'i man+dala zlum
NK013(pa)009:1808: po byas pa'i steng du bzhag /
NK013(pa)009:1809: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las khyad par lhag ma'i gnas su /
NK013(pa)009:1810: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da
NK013(pa)009:1811: la b+h+r+aum lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor mtshan nyid rdzogs par
NK013(pa)009:1812: gdan dang bcas pa'i nang gi dbus dang phyogs bzhir
NK013(pa)009:1817: rigs kyi yab lnga skad cig gis gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)009:1818: gtor ma dam tshig gsang ba'i longs spyod 'dod yon
NK013(pa)009:1819: gyi phung po zad mi shes pas nam mkha' gang
NK013(pa)009:1821: lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK013(pa)009:1822: h'u las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK013(pa)009:1823: mkha' 'gro lhag sdud ma sring ging gi tshogs //
NK013(pa)009:1824: lhag ma kha chu'i dam la gtogs pa rnams //
NK013(pa)009:1825: dam tshig bzhin du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)009:1826: ho mkha' 'gro gsang ba'i rgyud du gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK013(pa)009:1827: 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sngon gyi thugs dam dus
NK013(pa)009:1828: las mi 'da' bar sgrub pa'i sdong grogs la gshegs
NK013(pa)009:1829: shig / a ra li hrim hrim dzahmh'u bam hoh
NK013(pa)009:1830: d+aak+ki ni h'u dzah zhes brjod cing he ru ka'i
NK013(pa)009:1831: dam rgya dpral bar bcings nas spyug pa'i brda dang
NK013(pa)009:1833: mkha' 'gro so gnyis sprin gtibs pa bzhin byon te /
NK013(pa)009:1834: rigs lnga'i gtso bo la gtso mo bdun /
NK013(pa)009:1836: gzhan gsum la lnga lnga la dril zhing /
NK013(pa)009:1837: sgo ma bzhi gtso bo'i gdan gyi tshul du bzhugs ba la /
NK013(pa)009:1838: me togs la sogs pas spyir mchod nas /
NK013(pa)009:1839: dmar gyi rak+ta gtor ma la sbreng zhing he ru ka'i thod pa'i thal mo'i rgya dang bcas pas /
NK013(pa)009:1840: badz+ra d+aak+ki ni pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lim ta h'u phata /
NK013(pa)009:1841: de bzhin du bud+d+ha d+aak+ki ni sogs nas phata rat+na d+aak+ki ni sogs t+r+aam phata /
NK013(pa)009:1843: karma d+aak+ki ni sogs a phata /
NK013(pa)009:1844: ces pas gtor ma phul la /
NK013(pa)009:1845: h'u rnam dag chos dbyings zhi ba las //
NK013(pa)009:1846: thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa byung //
NK013(pa)009:1847: rang rang las kyis bskul gyur pas //
NK013(pa)009:1848: sprul pa bsam yas mkha' la 'gro /
NK013(pa)009:1851: mi ro skam po'i gdan steng la //
NK013(pa)009:1852: thugs rjes sprul pa cir yang ston //
NK013(pa)009:1853: mthing ga mi bskyod la sogs gzugs //
NK013(pa)009:1854: sum cu rtsa gnyis kun 'dzin zhing //
NK013(pa)009:1855: mi thod khrag gis bkang ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:1856: kha t+w+aam tri shul gshol gri bsnams //
NK013(pa)009:1857: rang rang lag cha sna tshogs ldan //
NK013(pa)009:1858: dpa' bo'i gzugs can kha mig bgrad //
NK013(pa)009:1859: nyi zla'i tshul du mkha' la 'gro //
NK013(pa)009:1860: zas su sha dang khrag dang ni //
NK013(pa)009:1861: rkang dang tshil bu rgyu ma za //
NK013(pa)009:1862: yang dag nyid de 'jig rten nyid //
NK013(pa)009:1863: sprul pa'i tshul gyis gzugs las sprul //
NK013(pa)009:1864: mkha' 'gro ma mo khyod rnams kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1865: sngon tshe bcom ldan rigs lnga la //
NK013(pa)009:1866: ye shes dbyings la chags tshul du /
NK013(pa)009:1868: / 'khril zhing rigs lnga'i slas su byas //
NK013(pa)009:1869: bstan pa bsrung bar mna' bor ba 'i //
NK013(pa)009:1870: khas blangs 'gal bar mi bya'i phyir //
NK013(pa)009:1871: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1873: h'u mkha' 'gro ging dang dbang phyug ma //
NK013(pa)009:1874: ma bdun sring bzhi 'bar ma brgyad //
NK013(pa)009:1875: pho nya la sogs lhag sdud tshogs //
NK013(pa)009:1876: dpal gyi pham phabs 'di gsol la //
NK013(pa)009:1877: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1878: ces brjod cing sman dang rak+tasa kyang mchod nas /
NK013(pa)009:1879: ho lhag sdud kyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK013(pa)009:1880: 'gro dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK013(pa)009:1881: rnams lhag ma'i dam tshig 'dis tshim zhing dgyes par
NK013(pa)009:1882: gyur te / dam tshig nyams chag thams cad bskangs nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK013(pa)009:1884: dge 'dun dang chos kyi rgyal srid skyong /
NK013(pa)009:1886: sems can gyi phan bde spel /
NK013(pa)009:1887: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi stong grogs mdzod /
NK013(pa)009:1888: sngags 'chang rnams kyi phrin las sgrubs /
NK013(pa)009:1889: khyad par dam tshig 'dir 'dus pa rnams kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang /
NK013(pa)009:1890: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa myur du 'grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK013(pa)009:1893: zhes pas mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam la /
NK013(pa)009:1894: gtor ma phyi rol du bskyal /
NK013(pa)009:1895: h'u zhes pas lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor rigs lnga rang la bstim nas /
NK013(pa)009:1897: gnyis pa brtan ma skyong ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1898: phyi rol du brtan ma'i gtor ma sman phud kyis bran la /
NK013(pa)009:1901: t+r+aam rat+na tree lo kya phata /
NK013(pa)009:1902: gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re bzhin rin po
NK013(pa)009:1903: che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi shes pas nam
NK013(pa)009:1906: h'u tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK013(pa)009:1907: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK013(pa)009:1908: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams /
NK013(pa)009:1910: / 'dir spyon dam skong phrin las mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1911: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1912: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1913: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK013(pa)009:1914: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK013(pa)009:1915: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK013(pa)009:1916: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK013(pa)009:1917: sil snyan rol mo'i sgra dang bcas /
NK013(pa)009:1919: / 'dir spyon dam skong phrin las mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1920: che zhe chen mo khyod rnams kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1921: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK013(pa)009:1923: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng ge yis //
NK013(pa)009:1924: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK013(pa)009:1925: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK013(pa)009:1926: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK013(pa)009:1927: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK013(pa)009:1928: bod khams srung zhing skyong ba dang //
NK013(pa)009:1929: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK013(pa)009:1930: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK013(pa)009:1931: g.yar dam gnyen po rjes dgongs la //
NK013(pa)009:1932: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK013(pa)009:1933: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)009:1938: ma ma srim 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo h'u h'u /
NK013(pa)009:1940: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta rak+ta b+ha lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK013(pa)009:1942: phrin las bcol nas ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs gsol byas la /
NK013(pa)009:1943: gtor ma gtsang sar bskyal lo //
NK013(pa)009:1944: gsum pa nyer bsdu bya ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1945: thun mtshams 'jug pa'am nyal ba na /
NK013(pa)009:1946: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he h'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa zhes pas dkyil 'khor gsal btabs la /
NK013(pa)009:1947: badz+ra pad+ma sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)009:1950: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK013(pa)009:1952: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK013(pa)009:1954: yab yum snyom par 'jug pa'i sbyor mtshams nas byang
NK013(pa)009:1955: chub sems kyi 'od zer gyi sprin 'phros pas snod
NK013(pa)009:1956: bcud thams cad dag cing 'od gsal bar bya /
NK013(pa)009:1957: sam ha ra na h'u zhes brjod pas dag pa'i
NK013(pa)009:1958: snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang srung 'khor dang
NK013(pa)009:1960: gzhal yas khang gi rgyan thams cad yab rnams la thim /
NK013(pa)009:1961: dngos po thams cad yum rnams la /
NK013(pa)009:1962: lha yab thams cad gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK013(pa)009:1963: yum thams cad dbyings phyug ma la /
NK013(pa)009:1965: de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK013(pa)009:1966: de ting nge 'dzin sems dpa' la /
NK013(pa)009:1968: h'u gyen rdzogs na da'i bar du thim nas rnam
NK013(pa)009:1969: par rtog med lhun grub nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang
NK013(pa)009:1971: nyal ba las langs pa'am spyod lam la 'jug pa ni /
NK013(pa)009:1973: ces brjod pas rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gcig phyag
NK013(pa)009:1974: gnyis pa snang stong sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i skur ldang
NK013(pa)009:1975: ngo / bzhi pa go cha bgo zhing lus srung ba ni /
NK013(pa)009:1976: rang nyid rdor sems su gsal ba'i spyi bor /
NK013(pa)009:1977: mgrin par +aah snying gar h'u yig rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK013(pa)009:1978: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha hamh zhes brjod pas lus
NK013(pa)009:1979: thams cad rdo rje rgya gram gyi go chas bzhu
NK013(pa)009:1980: lugs su g.yogs pas sgo gsum rdo rje gsum dang
NK013(pa)009:1981: dbyer med du bcings par bltas la /
NK013(pa)009:1982: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs /
NK013(pa)009:1983: sku gsung thugs kyis kun la khyab /
NK013(pa)009:1984: ces brjod cing nga rgyal bya /
NK013(pa)009:1985: de nas mdzub mo g.yas su t+r+aam las khro bo
NK013(pa)009:1986: rdo rje gnod sbyin nag po phyag gnyis kyis mche
NK013(pa)009:1988: g.yon du las khro bo mi 'chi thabs sbyor dmar
NK013(pa)009:1989: po rgya gram dang sdigs mdzub can du bskyed la
NK013(pa)009:1990: / lte ba snying ga ltag pa dang /
NK013(pa)009:1991: dpral ba spyi bo gnas lnga ru /
NK013(pa)009:1993: zhes brjod bzhin par mdzub mo gnyis bsnol nas rim par reg pas /
NK013(pa)009:1994: gnas de dang der khro bo gnyis po zung re
NK013(pa)009:1995: zhabs bsnol nas zhal phyir gzigs te srung ba'i las
NK013(pa)009:1996: mdzad pa'i thugs ka nas rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK013(pa)009:1997: byung bas bsrungs shing brtan par byas la /
NK013(pa)009:1998: rarna mu ku ta a b+hi shiny+tsa tram t+r+aam zhes rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur bar mos /
NK013(pa)009:1999: rat+na m+aa le a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram /
NK013(pa)009:2000: rin po che'i phreng ba bcings par bsam mo //
NK013(pa)009:2001: +aa r+ya lam b+ho d+ha ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aim
NK013(pa)009:2002: h+r+aimh dar mthing dmar gyi cod pan gyis brgyan par
NK013(pa)009:2003: bsam mo // gu h+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)009:2004: zhes brtan par bsam zhing yi ge brgya pa lan
NK013(pa)009:2005: gsum la sogs par bzlas pas shin tu brtan par
NK013(pa)009:2006: byas la / dge ba bsngo zhing bkra shis brjod pa rnams kyis mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK013(pa)009:2009: cho gas bstan pa'i thun dang mtshams kyi nges pa thams cad du /
NK013(pa)009:2010: phyin drug gi yan lag bskyed rdzogs kyi dngos por sdud pa las mi 'da' na /
NK013(pa)009:2011: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs myur du rdzogs par 'gyur la /
NK013(pa)009:2012: de yang rdo rje theg pa'i grub mtha' las dang /
NK013(pa)009:2015: phyag chen te phyag rgya bzhi'i sgo nas slong ba
NK013(pa)009:2016: la mnyam rjes kun tu bslabs pas rim pa dang
NK013(pa)009:2017: po'i dag rdzogs smin gsum lhongs su gyur nas skye
NK013(pa)009:2018: gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong zhing /
NK013(pa)009:2019: mngon par byang chub pa'i gzugs kyi sku myur du 'grub la /
NK013(pa)009:2020: de yang snga 'gyur rang gzhung gi grub mtha' lam lnga dang /
NK013(pa)009:2021: sa bcu'i spangs rtogs rig 'dzin bzhi'i go 'phang la
NK013(pa)009:2022: brten nas rdzogs pa'i tshul pan+di ta rong pa chos
